quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  21,45,"Maaku: "Anndu ko mi woni jeertinirde on ko Wahyu on, [kono] paho on nanataa noddaandu ndu, si …ďe njertinaama"."
  21,46,"Mi wo…óndii si meemii …ďe see…óa immorde e Lepte Joomi maa …óen, maa …ďe mbi'a: "Ee-yoo, bone amen pellet, minen min laatinoke too√Ī…ďe"."
  21,47,"Min mba…óa manndikir…óe(peesir…óe) Nuun…óal ngal fii √Ďande Darngal hara woŇčkii woo to√Īiroytaake hay e hu'unde, hay si laatii ko yeru gabbun pamarun Min ngaddat kum Min njonii Hasboo…ďe."
  21,48,"GooŇč…óii Min ngokkii Muusaa e Haaruuna Serndoore nden e ndayngu e jaŇčta wonan'de huloo…ďe …ďen."
  21,49,"∆Āe hulay…ďe Joomi ma…ď…ďe ka wirnii hara kam…ďe immorde e Darngal ngal ko …ďe kuli."
  21,50,"Ndee [Alqur‚Äôaanaare] ko nde JaŇčta, ko nde barkinaande Min nJippiniinde. Kaa onon ko on yeddat…ďe nde?"
  21,51,"GoŇč…óii Min ngkkii Ibraahiima Peewal makko ngal ko adii, Min laatike kadi Anndu…ďe mo."
  21,52,"Tuma nde o maakannoo baaba makko e yim…ďe makko …ďe: "Ko hol…óum woni …óii nanndonlaaji nate mahii…óe, …óin …ói ufini…óon e [dewal] mu'un?""
  21,53,"∆Āe mbi'i: "Min taw baabiraa…ďe amen …ďe no rewde …ói"."
  21,54,"O maaki: "GooŇč…óii on laatike onon e baabiraa…ďe mon …ďe e ndeer majjere …ďanngunde ngon…óon"."
  21,55,"∆Āe mbi'i: "Enee, ko Goonga kan addan…óaa min, kaa an ko e fijoo…ďe …ďe njeya…óaa?""
  21,56,"Maaku: "Ko woni, Joomi mo'on ko Jooma kammuuji …óin e leydi ndin oon Tagk…óo…ói, min komi jeyaa…óo e seedii…ďe …ďe e dow …óuum"."
  21,57,"Mi woo…óndirii Alla, maa mi fewja fii …óii sanamuuji mo'on …ďaawo duŇčtagolmo'on ko on ruŇčii …ďe."